<h3>D. Key Configuration Parameters</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>RAM Scale</strong>: 0.1-10.0 multiplier for cache sizes (default 1.0)</li>
  <li><strong>Archival Mode</strong>: Keep all historical data (no pruning)</li>
  <li><strong>UTXO Index</strong>: Enable address-based UTXO queries</li>
  <li><strong>Unsafe RPC</strong>: Allow state-modifying RPC commands</li>
  <li><strong>Enable Unsynced Mining</strong>: Allow mining while not synced (for network bootstrap)</li>
  <li><strong>Retention Period Days</strong>: Custom pruning policy (days of data to retain)</li>
  <li><strong>Block Template Cache Lifetime</strong>: Duration to cache mining templates (milliseconds)</li>
</ul>
